Pineapple Salsa

2 cups pineapple, diced
½ cup cilantro, chopped
¼ cup red onion, chopped
1 serrano pepper, chopped
1 lime, juiced
salt

Makes four servings of salsa.

Combine everything including salt to taste in a bowl and mix well. Refrigerate for 10 minutes to let flavors set.

Serve chilled with taro chips.
